Executive Compensation
As Senior Vice President and GM, Cable Products at HARMONIC INC, Nimrod  Ben-Natan  made $747,434 in total compensation.  Of this total $315,144 was received as a salary, $35,390 was received as a bonus, $77,632 was received in stock options, $233,401 was awarded as stock and $85,867 came from other types of compensation. This information is according to proxy statements filed for the 2016 fiscal year. 


